						<div class="postbody">On MD you have a <span class="posthilit">vertical</span> scroll table aswell, though its not <span class="posthilit">line</span> based but you can modify it midframe, that's how Road Rash games do their hills and numerous other games some <span class="posthilit">vertical</span> scaling effects (Mega Turrican and High Seas Havok coming to mind).</div>

					
